    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>Your friend Toby is upset that you’re moving and now won’t let you leave. Uncover secrets hidden around your house to stop Toby and finally put an end to this friendship.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quick!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get yourself ready before the lights go out.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/0753cd6eafd56ebf19b0485d2fb12e43.poster.avif?t=1764301937\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/0753cd6eafd56ebf19b0485d2fb12e43.webm?t=1764301937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/0753cd6eafd56ebf19b0485d2fb12e43.mp4?t=1764301937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Watch your step!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stepping on hard surfaces could grab unwanted attention.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/81a97341a85a45644390fe9cd8cdf444.poster.avif?t=1764301937\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/81a97341a85a45644390fe9cd8cdf444.webm?t=1764301937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/81a97341a85a45644390fe9cd8cdf444.mp4?t=1764301937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can’t run forever!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your Inhaler has limited puffs, so use it sparingly to keep your stamina accumulating quick enough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/f8cafa2c6dc90b8b0d014ec8c8386573.avif?t=1764301937\" width=609 height=512 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delay the inevitable by upgrading yourself with the points you earn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/82b276e286cc111f0372ddc6fdca40d5.poster.avif?t=1764301937\" width=608 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/82b276e286cc111f0372ddc6fdca40d5.webm?t=1764301937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/82b276e286cc111f0372ddc6fdca40d5.mp4?t=1764301937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Brand new mode!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095680/extras/3c3dd02da8197e2db0ce7a15e6aa8555.avif?t=1764301937\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself trapped inside Toby’s twisted playhouse. With nowhere to go but down, what awaits you at the bottom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go down random floors, completing random challenges, while also trying your best not to make a sound!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play part 1 now!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This game includes:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Main map with objectives, boss fight, and an ending</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus survival map </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Toby’s Twisted Playhouse Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional challenges for each survival map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stunning art style</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
